sentence: what are the cheapest round trip fares from montreal
sq2:
SELECT DISTINCT  v0.round_trip_cost, '"'||v6.fare_id||'"', '"'||v7.flight_id||'"',
 '"'||v8.airport_code||'"', '"'||v9.city_code||'"',
 '"'||v9.city_name||'"' FROM fare v0, flight_fare v6,
 flight v7, airport_service v8, city v9 
WHERE ((v0.round_trip_cost = (
SELECT MIN (v1.round_trip_cost) FROM fare v1 
WHERE (v1.fare_id IN (
SELECT v2.fare_id FROM flight_fare v2 
WHERE (v2.flight_id IN (
SELECT v3.flight_id FROM flight v3 
WHERE (v3.from_airport IN (
SELECT v4.airport_code FROM airport_service v4 
WHERE (v4.city_code IN (
SELECT v5.city_code FROM city v5 
WHERE (v5.city_name = 'MONTREAL'))))))))))) AND ((v0.fare_id = ANY v6.fare_id) 
AND ((v6.flight_id = ANY v7.flight_id) 
AND ((v7.from_airport = ANY v8.airport_code) AND ((v8.city_code = ANY v9.city_code) 
AND (v9.city_name = 'MONTREAL'))))));
